To open the class diagram found in docs/Classes.zargo you must use the ArgoUML
editor, which can be downloaded (for free) from http://argouml.tigris.org/

To compile the project in an Unix system you will need:

    - perl 5.10 (or later)
    - cmake 2.6 (or later)
    - make 3.81 (or later)

And use the commands, in this order:

$ ./configure
$ make

